- Designers shall collaborate with Region Transportation Operations and obtain theirconcurrence early in project development in the Work Zone Designer Strategy Meeting. The length of regulatory speed limit reductions shall be minimized to the extent possible, beginning no more than ½ mile prior to the restrictive roadway feature or condition, with the existing speed limit restored within 500 feet afterwards.[[SRC_2]]

