- If the weekly average of your turbidity monitoring results exceeds the standardbenchmark (or your approved alternate benchmark), you are required to conduct follow-up corrective action in accordance with Part 5.2.2 and document any corrective action taken in your corrective action log in accordance with Part 5.4.[[SRC_6]]

